Sovereign Solutions - Vaccine Liberation

In early production of Sovereign Solutions, producer Rich Angell interviews Vaccine Liberation Founder and Director Ingri Cassel, and Web Master Dewy Duffel, who present fascinating and enlightening information about vaccines that the medical industry doesn't want you know.
